In the Matter of Ralph WILSON, Bankrupt-Appellant. No. 293. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 18, 1938. Arnold S. Greene, of New York City, for appellant. __ S. Earl Levene, of New York City (Émanuel S. Cahn, of New York City, of counsel), for respondent.
